            "title": "外匯基金上半年錄得1944億元投資收入",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金管局公布，外匯基金於上半年錄得1944億元投資收入，當中753億元來自債券投資，港股投資收益也達229億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15137579-%e5%a4%96%e5%8c%af%e5%9f%ba%e9%87%91%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e9%8c%84%e5%be%971944%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5-2",
